Look up reviews for the best Buffalo Ranch Chicken Pizza in the area.
Choose the top rated location (no less than 4.7 stars)
Order one Large Buffalo Ranch Chicken Pizza with an extra side of Ranch.
(If they are out of this pizza thats ok just order one large classic crust chicken bacon ranch pizza still with the extra side of ranch.)
Order one medium thin crust Pepperoni Pizza.
Also add an order of garlic bread sticks.
Along with the garlic bread stick order some garlic sauce.
This order is for pickup.
Dont forget to check the order when it is picked up.
TIP!!
Remember to leave an honest review.